Developer Terms of Use
des:
"United State History Quiz" is an Alexa skill designed to test your general knowledge about U.S. history.
Users are asked questions about U.S. History and must answer with a "yes" or "no." Each time the user guesses the answer, they earn one point. Every ten questions the user's point will be announced.
The multiplayer mode supports up to two players.
In the multiplayer mode each 20 questions will reveal the players' scores.
